{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"symbolKind":"struct","platforms":[{"introducedAt":"15.0","unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"iOS"},{"introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"macOS"},{"introducedAt":"16.0","unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"tvOS"},{"introducedAt":"1.0","unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"visionOS"},{"introducedAt":"11.0","unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"watchOS"}],"role":"symbol","title":"OUDSTag","roleHeading":"Structure","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents7OUDSTagV","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"OUDSTag","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Indicators"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Appearances","level":2,"text":"Appearances","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags have two appearances so as to highlight or not their content:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"emphasized"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a solid, high-contrast background. Used to draw strong attention to important"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"labels or categories. Emphasized tags stand out prominently against the interface and are ideal for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"primary or high-priority information."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"muted"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a subtle, light, or semi-transparent background. Used for secondary or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"less prominent information. Muted tags blend more with the background, providing a softer visual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"emphasis compared to emphasized tags."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Status","text":"Status"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags have seven status depending on the context of the information they represent. Each state is designed","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to convey a specific meaning and ensure clarity in communication.","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Neutral"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Default or inactive state. Used for standard labels, categories, or when no specific"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"status needs to be communicated."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Accent"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Used to draw attention to new features, recommendations, or content suggestions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Invites users to explore and engage with new offerings, creating an exciting and engaging experience."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Positive"}]},{"text":": Indicates success, confirmation, or a positive status. Commonly used to highlight","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"completed actions or approved items.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Warning"}]},{"text":": Signals caution or a potentially risky situation. Used to draw attention to items","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"requiring user awareness or intervention.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Negative"}]},{"text":": Represents errors, critical issues, or urgent attention needed. Used to highlight","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"problems or failed actions.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Info"}]},{"text":": Conveys informational messages or supplementary details. Used for neutral, helpful,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or contextual information.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Disabled"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Shows that the tag is inactive and cannot be interacted with. Appears faded or greyed out. This is not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"allowed when loader is activated."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Shape","text":"Shape","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags can have two shapes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Rounded"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with fully rounded corners, creating a pill-shaped appearance. Rounded"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"tags offer a softer and more approachable look, suitable for most modern interfaces."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Square","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with sharp, square corners. Squared tags provide a more formal, structured, or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"technical feel. They are often used in business contexts to label promotions, offers, or important notices."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Size","text":"Size","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags can have two sizes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Default","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": The standard tag size, suitable for most use cases and offering good readability."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Small","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A compact tag with reduced height and font size. Used when saving space is important or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when grouping elements visually."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Layout","text":"Layout","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There are four available layouts for tags:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text only"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that displays only text. Used for simple labels, categories, or keywords without additional visual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"elements."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Bullet"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a small indicator (dot) alongside the text. Used to show status, presence, or activity"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"next to the label."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Icon"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that includes an icon before the text. Used to visually reinforce the meaning of the tag,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as status, type, or action."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text + Loader","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that combines a loading spinner (or progress indicator) with text. Used to indicate that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a process or action related to the tag is in progress."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Text only with neutral status, for emphasized appearance with rounded shape in default size","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\",  status: .neutral(), appearance: .emphasized, shape: .rounded, size: .default)","    \/\/ Or also","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\")","    \/\/ Or from a localizale and a bundle","    OUDSTag(LocalizedStringKey(\"label_wording\"), bundle: Bundle.module)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(leading: .bullet)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with a custom decorative icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")))","    \/\/ If your layout is in RTL mode but your tag has an icon with another meaning because of bad orientation,","    \/\/ you can flip the icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"), flipIcon: true))","","    \/\/ Text with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(bullet: true))","","    \/\/ Tag with loader with rounded shape in small size","    OUDSTag(loadingLabel: \"Label\", shape: .rounded, size: .small)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-tag","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"anchor":"Orange","text":"Orange","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_tag_Orange","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Orange-Compact","text":"Orange Compact","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_tag_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Sosh","text":"Sosh","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_tag_Sosh","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Wireframe","text":"Wireframe","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_tag_Wireframe","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","name":"Version","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.5.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}],"type":"aside"},{"style":"note","name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.18.0"}]}],"type":"aside"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstag"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tag is a UI element that allows to display short info like a label, keyword, or category."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Tag helps users quickly find, group, or understand content."}],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Structures","title":"Structures","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Status"],"generated":true},{"anc